# Tailwind CSS v4

- Entry point: `src/app/index.css` with `@import "tailwindcss"`
- Uses `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin; no separate `tailwind.config.js` by default
- Prefer utility classes over custom CSS
- Use `@layer` for custom utilities/components if needed
- Add theme extensions via `@theme` in CSS when customizing
